{"tid":2290920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2020年既TVB一點收視=225000人；2015年仲係65000人","createTime":"2020-11-18T11:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T15:50:58.000Z","uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"714c0ed9c9a4483c030a586c7f56a6606d1794d0","tid":2290920,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2020年<br />\n有鑑全港電視將於12月1日轉為全數碼廣播制式，因應廣播模式改變，無綫電視（TVB）公布收視的方式也有所不同。今日（11月16日）更在翡翠台廣告時段公開各個電視台在2020年1-10月的收視。根據CSM收視調查，黃金時段晚上7點至10點，翡翠台的數碼直播收視為20.6點（接觸觀眾近450萬），J2台有1.9點，新聞台有2.4點，而ViuTV99台於同時段則有2.1點，開電視則有1.2點。<br />\n<br />\n2015年<br />\n而據TVB資料，2015年的總電視人口為646.6萬人，每一個收視點代表總電視人口的百分之一，即6.5萬人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20151026/5NPC3NZHWHPLFST752ZEJ5IOUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20151026%2F5NPC3NZHWHPLFST752ZEJ5IOUE%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1T4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=7a90d876\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20151026%2F5NPC3NZHWHPLFST752ZEJ5IOUE%2F&h=3c92cbb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20151026/5NPC3NZHWHPLFST752ZEJ5IOUE/</a>"},{"pid":"f7f61671030b2db279715a335ee9d8b719b95c94","tid":2290920,"uid":22556,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182c98eb0a7ca331df9c41e74cf36a36ac9c2af3","tid":2290920,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f7f61671030b2db279715a335ee9d8b719b95c94","tid":2290920,"uid":22556,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci